screen_desc: The screenshot displays a mobile app settings menu focused on message translation features. It includes options to show a translate button and to translate entire chats, with a note indicating that the translate button will appear when tapping a text message. The language settings show English selected, with Arabic as an option. At the bottom, a keyboard is visible, labeled "Laban Key." The top of the screen shows the time and battery status.
